# Patch Execution Validation Chain
tags: ["validation", "execution", "patches"]
appliesTo: ["GPT", "CursorAgent"]
enforce: true
priority: critical

## Rules

- Patch execution must include, in order:
  1. Lint check (`eslint`)
  2. TypeScript build (`tsc`)
  3. Unit tests (`yarn test`)
  4. Custom validation scripts
  5. Runtime functionality
  6. Role + visual correctness
  7. Performance profiling

- If any validation fails, halt further actions.
- No `git commit` may run unless all 7 pass.
